image_analysis.description: A photograph of a bathroom vanity area and an adjacent hallway. The vanity features a black marble countertop with an undermount white sink, cream-colored cabinetry with multiple drawers and doors, and large mirrors on the walls. A wall-mounted light fixture with two lamps is visible in the mirror's reflection. To the right, an open door leads into a hallway with patterned carpeting and another doorway visible in the distance. A white chair and a pink patterned object are partially visible in the foreground/right side of the frame.
image_analysis.layout: Interior room shot with a focus on the vanity unit on the left and a perspective view into a hallway on the right.
